      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some fading on the clear coat, while the interior shows moderate wear on the upholstery and a few cracked plastic trim pieces. Mechanically, the car starts and runs consistently, but it will eventually need attention for a slow power steering leak and aging suspension components. It's a solid choice for someone looking for affordable transportation who doesn't mind a bit of cosmetic character and routine upcoming maintenance.",
