      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of the high-revving S54 platform. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six features a crisp throttle response via its individual throttle bodies, with the dual-VANOS system recently overhauled for optimal cam timing. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a rod bearing service. Power is managed through a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec M-Variable differential lock. The suspension geometry remains tight with upgraded bushings, providing the tactile feedback and lateral grip expected of this chassis. A well-sorted driver\u2019s car ready for the apex.",
